    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is a total dream! This car is in truly incredible shape; honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every maintenance schedule. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take it for a spin, I promise you'll fall in love immediately!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
