      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a purist's specification featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example exhibits exceptional mechanical hygiene; the rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The double-VANOS system operates with surgical precision, providing a seamless power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis retains its factory-spec dampening and bushings, offering the tactile, communicative steering rack feedback these cars are renowned for. The exterior finish remains in showroom state, free of rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior's Nappa leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
